:29:45.000Z","msg":"海狗準備做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17011f4721a3d8dff73b728ff3bf9fbce2406ab5","tid":2435583,"uid":51183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4abce462996ef7068148810738df59797bf1d324","tid":2435583,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"海狗準備做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:38:06.000Z","msg":"香港的基本食物法例載於香港法例第132章第V部（食物及藥物）《公眾衛生及市政條例》。食物環境衛生署負責實施食物安全監管政策和執行有關法例。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">為確保所入口的食物符合香港法例的規定，食物入口商應先向來源地衛生當局申領衛生證明書</span>，然後將證明書隨貨附上，以證明所入口的食物適宜供人食用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下又點搬龍門先"},{"pid":"a06ab98165ef47b307e24f7f1610138c62bf5822","tid":2435583,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:39:54.000Z","msg":"想食菠蘿都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b4f03ff3f6cd5587a3e037b11bc29f992f8fe5","tid":2435583,"uid":51621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7395ca4ced5082358b3fde804f17fa83b766fa3f","tid":2435583,"uid":104035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"起因就係要報復台灣唔畀向狗移民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"台灣波羅3月係收成期.<br />\n台灣波羅年產量1/10會出口,當中90%係出口去中國,<br />\nso,佢想攪9台灣果農only"}]}